    public class AttachmentMapper
extends org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.FieldMapper
          "field1" : "..."

    Or: 

     {
      "file1" : {
          "_content_type" : "application/pdf",
          "_content_length" : "500000000",
          "_name" : "..../something.pdf",
          "_content" : ""
      }
 }

    _content_length = Specify the maximum amount of characters to extract from the attachment. If not specified, then the default for tika is 100,000 characters. Caution is required when setting large values as this can cause memory issues.
